<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西向朋友们大声喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>朋友们已经走远了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很快就回来！我还没找到我的水壶！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等！”特勒尔回答道，“我们可以帮忙……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在特勒尔说完之前，罗西已经跑不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很快就飞向天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”玛拉大喊，“是火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们看到火箭女孩儿的时候，罗西总是不在。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西到了真实储蓄银行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>前面停着警车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>银行里面，史密斯侦探站在柜台后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先生， 您好！”罗西说，“我想开户。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探皱起了眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很有意思，火箭女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，我们有一个案子要破。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这家银行被抢劫了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。”罗西说，“您知道强盗是谁吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是刚到的。我正在找线索。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“强盗不止一个。”一个保安跑过来说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们有一伙。他们真的太可怕了，又脏又丑又凶！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探从口袋里掏出一个小本子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能描述一下他们的长相吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>保安点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“强盗头目戴着一顶大帽子，手上有一个钩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121737</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只鹦鹉坐在她的肩上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鹦鹉不停地说‘哟呵呵’！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探扬起一边的眉毛。“哟呵呵？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对的！”保安说，“哟呵呵。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别的强盗长什么样子呢？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>保安摸了摸下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“其他的三个强盗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个留着长胡子，戴着一只眼罩；</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另外两人戴着头巾，一个人有一条木腿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听起来像是海盗！”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探挠了挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“美罗城没有海盗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们一定是从别的地方来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在他们抢劫另外一家银行之前，我们必须阻止他们。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，史密斯侦探的电话响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂？天啊！好的，我们马上赶过去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生什么事了？”罗西问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些海盗又抢了别的银行了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是！”史密斯侦探说，“他们正在吃午饭。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯？”罗西糊涂了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些海盗在‘码头餐厅’。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是城里最高档的海鲜餐厅。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探说，“餐厅老板说他们惹了很多麻烦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把餐厅搞得一团糟，摔东西，威胁别的客人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西双臂交叉。“我们得去抓他们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探把手机放进口袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，火箭女孩儿。我们……火箭女孩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>